flowchart TB
    Premium[Gross Written Premium<br/>1,000 USD]

    Premium --> PurePrem[Pure Premium<br/>650 USD<br/>65%]
    Premium --> LAE[Loss Adjustment Expense<br/>80 USD<br/>8%]
    Premium --> Acquisition[Acquisition Costs]
    Premium --> General[General Expenses<br/>50 USD<br/>5%]
    Premium --> Taxes[Premium Taxes &<br/>Regulatory Fees<br/>25 USD<br/>2.5%]
    Premium --> Profit[Profit & Contingency<br/>65 USD<br/>6.5%]

    Acquisition --> Commission[Commission to<br/>Agents / Brokers<br/>100 USD<br/>10%]
    Acquisition --> OtherAcq[Other Acquisition<br/>30 USD<br/>3%]

    PurePrem --> ExpectedLoss{Expected Claims<br/>to Policyholders}
    LAE --> ClaimsHandling{Claims Dept<br/>& Adjusters}

    ExpectedLoss -.Subject to.-> Variance[Actual losses may vary<br/>from pure premium]
    Variance -->|Favorable| Profit2[Underwriting profit<br/>above target]
    Variance -->|Adverse| Loss2[Underwriting loss<br/>eats into surplus]

